          </svg>
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded mt-4 mb-4 p-2 w-fit mx-auto">
            <h1 class="px-2 text-[#204c86] font-opensans">A UX that adjusts to you</h1>
          </div>
          <p class="font-normal text-slate-600 text-[15px] font-lato">A good interface should get out of the way and give you quick access to the things you need most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#f7f8fd] text-[17px] w-[22rem] p-6 rounded shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" fill="#2C85EF" class="m-auto bi bi-ui-checks-grid" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
