          </svg>
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded mt-4 mb-4 p-2 w-fit mx-auto">
            <h1 class="px-2 text-[#204c86] font-opensans">Control everything</h1>
          </div>
          <p class="font-normal text-slate-600 text-[15px] font-lato">Your site, your style. Our extensive customization options let you create a site that's uniquely yours. Get the information you need, exactly when you need it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#f7f8fd] text-[17px] w-[22rem] p-6 rounded shadow-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" fill="#2C85EF" class="m-auto bi bi-chat-dots" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M5 8a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0zm4 0a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0zm3 1a1 1 0 1 0 0-2 1 1 0 0 0 0 2z"/>
